item.title: SoftLayer_Network_ContentDelivery_Authentication_Address
item.description: SoftLayer_Network_ContentDelivery_Authentication_Address Service Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Network_ContentDelivery_Authentication_Address data type models an individual IP address that CDN allow or deny access from. Local accessType The type of access on an IP address. It can be "ALLOW" or "DENY" Type: string cdnAccountId The internal identifier of the CDN account Type: integer createDate The created date Type: dateTime id The internal identifier of an authentication IP address Type: integer
